157
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,640
Tahulah.

158
00:10:23,160 --> 00:10:24,440
Saya dah besar.

159
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:28,000
Saya pandai berfikir sendiri, menganalisis dan menilai.

160
